There is no doubt that the HCI community plays an important role in raising the awareness and the importance of good web design,</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="3" relname="volitional-cause"> but since any one with little computer knowledge and probably with no web design knowledge can develop and publish a web site,</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="11" relname="span"> we will continue to see more and more poorly designed web sites.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="13" relname="span"> 
